---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import DisclaimerBanner from '../components/DisclaimerBanner.astro';
import StickyMobileBookingCTA from '../components/StickyMobileBookingCTA.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Terms & Disclaimer', href: '/terms-and-disclaimer' }
];
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions | Rabbia Psychologist">
  <SEO
    title="Terms and Conditions | Rabbia Psychologist"
    description="Read the terms, service boundaries, professional disclaimer, payment notes, privacy limits, and international family guidance for Rabbia Psychologist Child Development Services."
  />
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <Breadcrumbs paths={breadcrumbs} />
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 max-w-none">

        <div class="mb-8">
          <p>Please review our terms carefully. By using our services, you agree to these terms.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4">
            <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-brand-navy underline">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/refund-cancellation-policy" class="text-brand-navy underline">Refund and Cancellation Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/service-delivery-policy" class="text-brand-navy underline">Service Delivery Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="text-brand-navy underline">Contact page</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8 border border-gray-300">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-0">Professional Disclaimer</h2>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy">
            Rabbia Psychologist Child Development Services provides parent guidance, educational resources, developmental support planning, report review support, school guidance, and between-session parent support programs.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            These services are not emergency services.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            Online support does not replace local medical, psychological, educational, legal, crisis, or school-based services.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            Between-session support programs are designed to support parent understanding, home carryover, routines, and practical implementation. They do not guarantee outcomes and do not replace direct therapy, diagnosis, emergency care, or local regulated services where required.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            Regulated services are provided only within the professional scope, credentials, and legal requirements of the professional and client location.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4 italic">

          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Nature of services</h2>
        <p>International support may include parent education, developmental guidance, ASD/ADHD support planning, behavior strategy discussion, executive-function routines, school communication preparation, resource guidance, and referral direction.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Booking and payment</h2>
        <p>Payment is required to confirm appointments. We use authorized third-party gateways for secure processing.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Client responsibilities</h2>
        <p>Clients are expected to provide accurate information and ensure a private environment and stable internet connection for online sessions.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Cancellation and refunds</h2>
        <p>Please review our <a href="/refund-cancellation-policy" class="text-brand-navy underline">Refund and Cancellation Policy</a>. A minimum 24-hour notice is typically required.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Service delivery</h2>
        <p>Please refer to our <a href="/service-delivery-policy" class="text-brand-navy underline">Service Delivery Policy</a> for details on online and in-person service provisions.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Online consultation limitations</h2>
        <p>Clinical therapy, diagnosis, assessment, and regulated psychological services are provided only where legally and ethically permitted by the professional's credentials and the client's location.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Report and assessment limitations</h2>
        <p>Formal assessments and diagnostic reports are provided according to specific service agreements. Results and recommendations are based on the data available at the time.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Emergency disclaimer</h2>
        <p>Online parent consultation is not appropriate for emergency situations or acute crises. In the event of a medical or psychological emergency, please contact your local emergency services or proceed to the nearest hospital.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>All content, materials, and resources provided on this website and during consultations remain our intellectual property and are for personal use only.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Digital products</h2>
        <p>Digital products and downloadable resources are strictly non-refundable and are meant for personal educational use.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Website use</h2>
        <p>The information on this website is for general educational guidance and does not replace professional consultation.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Privacy</h2>
        <p>We respect your privacy. See our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-brand-navy underline">Privacy Policy</a> for how we handle your data.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Payment disputes</h2>
        <p>Any disputes regarding payments should be communicated to us promptly so we can review the issue.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Governing law</h2>
        <p>These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of Pakistan, and any disputes will be subject to its jurisdiction.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Contact information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, please reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-navy underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <StickyMobileBookingCTA />
</Layout>
